integers, we could say.

113
00:04:50,857 --> 00:04:52,440
Whole number, it's
not a whole number,

114
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,400
because that's just the
natural numbers and 0.

115
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:57,240
It is an integer.

116
00:04:57,240 --> 00:05:00,030
It is the opposite
of positive 15.

117
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:03,360
It is an integer.

118
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:07,240
It is rational, it can be
represented as 15 over 1.

119
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,710
